The paper discusses a system for preserving computational context and providing end users with a self-contained environment, which is relevant to several sub-categories. cs.CY (Computers and Society) is the most likely category as the paper discusses the importance of reproducibility in research. cs.DL (Digital Libraries) is also relevant as the paper discusses the concept of an executable paper. cs.SE (Software Engineering) is relevant as the paper discusses the challenges of releasing code and ensuring reproducibility. cs.DB (Databases) is relevant as the paper discusses the importance of preserving data and computational context. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is relevant as the paper discusses the challenges of finding and reusing research results.
